&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="/articles/0030/0671/libreoffice.png" height="99" alt="" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="473"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span title="CloudOn joins The Document Foundation Advisory Board to Accelerate LibreOffice Availability on Mobile Devices"&gt;&lt;span title="CloudOn is a productivity platform that allows users to create, edit and share documents in real time across devices."&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="“We fully support The Document Foundation's core values and are honored to be part of this esteemed group,” says Jay Zaveri, VP, Products for CloudOn “This collaboration with the outstanding LibreOffice development team is fully aligned with the CloudOn vision and part of our"&gt;"Apoiamos plenamente os valores fundamentais da The Document Foundation e estamos honrados em fazer parte dessa fundação", diz Jay Zaveri, vice-presidente de Produtos para CloudOn". Esta colaboração com a equipe de desenvolvimento do LibreOffice é totalmente alinhados com a visão da CloudOn e parte do nosso &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="constant drive to offer tools that enable people to work smarter.”"&gt;movimentação constante para oferecer ferramentas que permitem que as pessoas trabalhem mais inteligentes ".&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="“It is fantastic to have CloudOn's depth of mobile experience and development muscle to work with."&gt;"É fantástico ter profundidade de experiência móvel e desenvolvimento forte para trabalhar com o CloudOn. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="I particularly like their emphasis on execution,” said Michael Meeks, VP Productivity at Collabora and TDF Board Member, “We are thrilled to be working alongside CloudOn, and are pleased to see the smooth way they have integrated into the community, with code already"&gt;Eu gosto particularmente da sua ênfase na execução", disse Michael Meeks, VP Produtividade no Collabora e Conselheiro da &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="I particularly like their emphasis on execution,” said Michael Meeks, VP Productivity at Collabora and TDF Board Member, “We are thrilled to be working alongside CloudOn, and are pleased to see the smooth way they have integrated into the community, with code already"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="I particularly like their emphasis on execution,” said Michael Meeks, VP Productivity at Collabora and TDF Board Member, “We are thrilled to be working alongside CloudOn, and are pleased to see the smooth way they have integrated into the community, with code already"&gt;TDF&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;".&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span title="I particularly like their emphasis on execution,” said Michael Meeks, VP Productivity at Collabora and TDF Board Member, “We are thrilled to be working alongside CloudOn, and are pleased to see the smooth way they have integrated into the community, with code already"&gt; Estamos entusiasmados por estar trabalhando ao lado de CloudOn e estamos satisfeitos por ver a sua integração com a comunidade, com o código já &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="included, and their participation in Engineering Steering Committee meetings.”"&gt;incluídos, e sua participação nas reuniões do Comitê Diretor de Engenharia."&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="With the addition of CloudOn, the Advisory Board of The Document Foundation now has 13 members: AMD, CloudOn, Collabora, FRODEV (Freies Office Deutschland eV), FSF (Free Software Foundation), Google, Intel, KACST (King Abdulaziz City of Science"&gt;Com a vinda da CloudOn, o Conselho Consultivo da The Document Foundation tem agora 13 membros: AMD, CloudOn, Collabora, FRODEV (Freies Escritório Deutschland eV), FSF (Free Software Foundation), Google, Intel, KACST (King Abdulaziz Cidade da Ciência &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="and Technology), Lanedo, MIMO (French Ministries), RedHat, SPI (Software in the Public Interest) and SUSE."&gt;e Tecnologia), Lanedo, MIMO (Ministério francês), RedHat, SPI (Software in the Public Interest) e SUSE.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="About CloudOn"&gt;Sobre CloudOn:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="CloudOn is a leading mobile productivity platform that allows users to create, edit and share documents in real time across devices."&gt;A CloudOn é uma instituição líder de produtividade móvel que permite aos usuários criar , editar e compartilhar documentos em tempo real através de dispositivos. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="With proven technology already trusted by over five million registered users globally, CloudOn is platform-agnostic and completely optimized for iOS, Android devices, as well as the web."&gt;Com a tecnologia já comprovada a confiança de mais de 5 milhões de usuários registrados no mundo, CloudOn é independente de plataforma e completamente otimizado para iOS, dispositivos Android, bem como a web. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="It also offers seamless integration with Box, Dropbox, Google Drive and SkyDrive."&gt;Também oferece integração com Box, Dropbox, Google Drive e SkyDrive.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="Media Contact CloudOn"&gt;Contato com a mídia CloudOn&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="Jenna Richard (based in San Francisco, California, UTC-7)"&gt;Jenna Richard (San Francisco - Califórnia)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title="Phone: +1 (415) 277-4927 – Email: CloudOn@allisonpr.com"&gt;Fone: +1 (415) 277-4927&lt;br&gt;E-mail: CloudOn@allisonpr.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
