&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span class="hps"&gt;Para&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hps"&gt;instalar e usar o&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hps"&gt;Impress&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hps"&gt;remoto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hps"&gt;você deve&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hps"&gt;primeiro fazer o download&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hps"&gt;do Google&lt;/span&gt; Play&lt;span class="hps"&gt; no seu&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hps"&gt;smartphone Android&lt;/span&gt; e depois &lt;span class="hps"&gt;seguir um procedimento&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hps"&gt;simples, que é&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hps"&gt;descrito na página&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href="https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Development/Impress/RemoteHowTo/pt-br" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span class="hps"&gt;Wiki&lt;/span&gt; da TDF&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="hps"&gt;e também&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="hps"&gt;neste vídeo:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt; &lt;iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/hM5H4fUxq4M?version=3&amp;amp;rel=1&amp;amp;fs=1&amp;amp;showsearch=0&amp;amp;showinfo=1&amp;amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;amp;wmode=transparent" frameborder="0" height="360" width="640"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
